title: Prog Magazine Radio Show Torrent #1 (progressive rock)
description:
The Prog Magazine Radio Show (Presented by TeamRock) Torrent #1
30 complete radio shows from 2014 (LAME 3.98r MP3s @ 244 kbps CBR)

Notes:

The Prog Magazine radio show hosted by Philip Wilding currently airs every Wednesday on the UK Internet radio platform TeamRock.  It started in 2014 airing on Saturdays and Sundays.  Each show features the best in current and classic progressive rock.  Some shows have interviews with prog luminaries and others feature prog legends guest hosting and choosing the music (for example, Steven Wilson/Tim Bowness and Steve Hogarth of Marillion).     

These MP3s were downloaded directly from the TeamRock website using a custom program written in Java (they are not currently visible on the site for streaming, but they are still on the site's servers, which was discovered through a bit of detective work).  The MP3s are original as found on the server, with no re-encoding performed (each show is about 2 hours long and 200 MB in size).
